&nbsp; <b>0.0.0.0 IN HOSTS:2009</b> -&gt; <a href="http://tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1143349&amp;cid=27012231" title="slashdot.org" rel="nofollow">http://tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=1143349&amp;cid=27012231</a> <span class="domain-text"> [slashdot.org]</span>  <br>
